---
title: Teriyaki Beef & Eggplant Stir Fry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description:  Power up with this protein-packed stir-fry! Tender beef mince and roasted eggplant come together in a deliciously rich sauce, served over fragrant garlic rice. A fresh sprinkle of coriander tops it all off, making this a hearty, flavour-filled meal that fuels your day.

